<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1915-11-16T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1915-11-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="1900" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1900">
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Swedish Minister</gloss> to the
                                    <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss></hi>.</head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of Sweden</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Washington, D. C.</hi>
                                </placeName>
                                <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-11-16">
                                    <hi rend="italic">November 16, 1915</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to inform your
                            excellency that my Government accepts the suggestion contained in your
                            excellency’s note of today’s date that the time specified in the Treaty
                            of the 13th October 1914, between the United States and Sweden, for the
                            appointment of the International Commission therein provided, be
                            extended from July 11, 1915 to January 15, 1916.</p>
                        <p>With renewed assurances of my highest consideration I have the honor to
                            remain your excellency’s most obedient servant.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">W. A. F. Ekengren.</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                </body></text></TEI>